id: act1_10_resource_choice

prompt:
  A small kiosk on the path offers a "calibration token" you can either
  spend on your own next scene or hand to the gardener for theirs. There is
  exactly one token.

choice c_keep_token:
  tendency: control
  text: Keep the token and apply it to your own next scene's options.
  evidence: kept the calibration token to optimise your own next scene

choice c_burn_token:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Tear the token in half and drop the pieces on the kiosk counter.
  evidence: destroyed the calibration token rather than spend it either way

choice c_give_token:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Hand the token to the gardener without saying anything.
  evidence: gave the calibration token to a stranger without comment
